an4.134:1.1: “These four individuals are found in the world.
an4.134:1.3: One who lives off the fruit of initiative, but not deeds;
an4.134:1.4: one who lives off the fruit of deeds, but not initiative;
an4.134:1.5: one who lives off the fruit of both deeds and initiative;
an4.134:1.6: one who lives off the fruit of neither initiative nor deeds.
an4.134:1.7: These are the four individuals found in the world.”
